	<h1 class="title">如果不被爱马仕收购，这个银器作坊会独自闯世界吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/399912/small/399912.JPG?1452046699" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张田小 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-06-08 16:49:15 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/10528/medium/10528.jpg?1436647859" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="10528" data-title="《如果不被爱马仕收购，这个银器作坊会独自闯世界吗？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/10528/medium/10528.jpg?1436647859" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/10528.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
